---
import MediaEmbed from '../../../components/MediaEmbed.astro';
---

  <section class="component-group" id="group-media">
    <header class="component-group__header">
      <h2>Media nhúng</h2>
      <p>Video/audio HTML5 hoặc iframe (YouTube, Vimeo, …). Luôn điền <code>title</code> cho accessibility.</p>
    </header>

  {/* ─────── MediaEmbed ─────── */}
  <section class="showcase-section" id="mediaembed">
    <h3>MediaEmbed</h3>
    <p>
      Prop <code>kind</code>: <code>video</code> | <code>audio</code> | <code>iframe</code>.
      Ví dụ video dùng sample CC0 từ MDN; iframe dùng <code>youtube-nocookie</code>.
    </p>
    <div class="example-render">
      <MediaEmbed
        kind="video"
        src="https://interactive-examples.mdn.mozilla.net/media/cc0-videos/flower.mp4"
        title="Demo video (MDN sample)"
        caption="Video minh hoạ — thay <code>src</code> bằng file báo cáo của bạn."
      />
    </div>
    <div class="example-render">
      <MediaEmbed
        kind="audio"
        src="https://interactive-examples.mdn.mozilla.net/media/cc0-audio/t-rex-roar.mp3"
        title="Demo audio (MDN sample)"
      />
    </div>
    <div class="example-render">
      <MediaEmbed
        kind="iframe"
        src="https://www.youtube-nocookie.com/embed/aqz-KE-bpKQ"
        title="Big Buck Bunny (Blender Foundation) — embed demo"
        caption="Iframe 16:9; chỉnh <code>aspectRatio</code> nếu khác."
      />
    </div>
    <pre class="example-code"><code>{`<MediaEmbed kind="video" src="https://..." title="Mô tả ngắn" caption="Caption HTML" />

<MediaEmbed kind="iframe" src="https://www.youtube-nocookie.com/embed/..." title="Video" />`}</code></pre>
  </section>

  </section>
